---
import ArchitectureFlow from '../react/ArchitectureFlow';
---

<section id="architecture" class="py-16 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-brand-border/80 transition-colors">
  <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="arch_title">透明、干净的双进程交互架构</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3" data-i18n="arch_subtitle">拒绝一切黑盒逻辑。这是 DeepFlow 的内部运行模式，让每一条数据流转都在你的控制之中。</p>
  </div>
  <ArchitectureFlow client:visible />
</section>
